Hi Jasonw,
The lower engine mounting studs are 10mm not 8mm!!!  The same as the upper 
engine mounting bolts.  As for the gas tank keep looking for a 1968-71 bus 15 
gallon tank and install a reserve switch for future no spill engine or fuel line 
changes.
